text: The instructions about it were: Welcome to the study! The goal of this discussion is for you to try to reach a consensus on the topic: Ketchup vs Mustard. In order to reach a consensus, the "I agree! message above has been pinned to the top of the discussion. Please give this message a thumbs up when you are happy with the state of the discussion, i.e, when you are in agreement, and when you believe the topic has been resolved. Remove the thumbs up when you are unhappy with the state of discussion. You can easily find this post by clicking on details, and then Pinned Items. This may be different on mobile devices. If you have trouble finding it, please contact me privately to ask for help. This can be done on Slack under the Direct messages section on the left of screen. We ask that you refrain from posting images, and that all things mentioned in this discussion are done with the intent to reach a consensus and not done to jeopardize the study
